{"tid":1508391,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「極重要」三大核彈 (使用篇)","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T07:01:58.000Z","uid":191271,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"855eefe2de7efabcef0a7fb848e8d6b7130c5023","tid":1508391,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">多謝大家，上個post反應熱烈 3000+正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「極重要」香港將影響世界50年發展+ 三大核彈方向</span><br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1497709/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1497709/page/1</a><br />\n決定行多步，寫埋真正有效既行動細則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYWaPn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYWaPn5.jpg&h=17bce35b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">***** 打飛機時間，沒興趣就飛， 直接睇下面三粒核彈點用 *****</span></span></strong><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78fKS0t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78fKS0t.jpg&h=a0d1515e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國前白宮策略師</span></strong>兼任Trump 總統顧問（2017年1月 - 8月）<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（Steve Bannon）</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係琴日<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月25日</strong></span>接受另一間媒體訪問，今次講到華為5G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />威脅全球論 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmtkrvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmtkrvV.jpg&h=e852d1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條片我沒時間睇哂，而且沒任何字幕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uCrpSK5r9HY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuCrpSK5r9HY&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=d7083d87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uCrpSK5r9HY</a><br />\n<br />\n但重點就係 36: 54 - 37:54 呢一分鍾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Steve Bannon (真。前美國國師)<br />\n公開呼籲提名香港抗爭者獲得諾貝爾和平獎。</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(白官聯署係有效，美國國會係會睇，你將會係美國國會議員既Twitter發現更多)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下係我譯呢一分鍾既廣東話版</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/26/005916_8264a6a652925655eb785a23a0150cf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2F005916_8264a6a652925655eb785a23a0150cf7.png&h=4ddf69f6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n班農: 當提及到香港人，我想講，宜家我地社會成日批評80/90/00後，話佢地懶、唔專心、乜都要人幫，但我會講同你講，唔該，Hey, 請你睇下香港，<span style=\"color: pink;\">睇下香港既年輕人，<br />\n我係佢地身上見到1776年帶領美國獨立戰爭既先烈意志。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">呢班年輕人有堅毅不屈既決心、所向披靡、無所畏懼。</span><br />\n警察曾經向佢地發射過無數既tear gas， 甚至橡膠子彈，受警棍既毆打，<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">但一次又一次，佢地用行動證明比我地睇: </span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚驚過</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我認為佢地係當代既英雄，佢地係應該被提名再攞埋諾貝爾和平獎,</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">因為香港既抗爭者向世人展示出一個有自由意志既人，<br />\n面對極權既打壓毫不示弱，挺身而出既精神，呢班人不單止係所有年輕人既榜樣，<br />\n係都所有人既榜樣</span>，所以我覺得香港抗爭者非常偉大，歷史就係我地眼前上映，<br />\n香港所發生既一切，Every day將會記載入歷史。<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nInterviewee: You know speaking of Hong Kong based on everything you just said <br />\nit doesn't look good for the people of Hong Kong. What do you think?<br />\n<br />\nBannon: I think the people of Hong Kong, Um, you know people always trash the Millennials <br />\nas they are lazy, they are unfocused they want everything handed to them. <span style=\"color: pink;\">I say<br />\nHey, look at the Millennials in Hong Kong those young men and women are exactly what<br />\nthe Patriots of 1776 were in the United States. </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">They have the grit, They have the determination, They have the indefatigable ability. They are not going to back down.</span><br />\n<br />\nThey've been tear-gassed. They've been beaten. They've been rubber bullets shot at them. And <span style=\"color: pink;\">Time and Time again</span>,  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">they show up. </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nI think they're heroes the modern world. <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">I think they deserve to be nominated for and win the Nobel Prize for Peace</span></span> <span style=\"color: green;\">  because they have shown what free men and women will do to stand up against a totalitarian dictatorship and they are a lesson not just for this age but for all ages</span> and that's why I think it's so remarkable what's going on. We are seeing history made in real time and what's going on in Hong Kong every day is making history.<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔好意思，香港抗爭者就係咁舉世矚目</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(按:香港抗爭者 - 《TIME》互聯網25大具影響力人物)<br />\n<br />\n居港幾年的西班牙人Matthew: <br />\n「你們知道，<span style=\"color: teal;\">在歐洲所有人都在討論你們香港人嗎？You guys are the inspiration of the world（你們啟發了世界）</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<ins>既然全世界99%外媒都讚緊，連登熱門更加應該有更多稱讚真勇武，和理非既POST </ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登全體心聲：感謝勇武 19000 + 正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1504748/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1504748/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有更重要既係<br />\n街上群眾英雄式既 歡呼鼓掌!!! <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">825 沙田</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=77xWR0agV2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D77xWR0agV2I&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=21877a1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=77xWR0agV2I</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">811美孚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TGVD6aMMhbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTGVD6aMMhbo&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=70f31f25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TGVD6aMMhbo</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">我正式宣佈</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xNYdJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xNYdJK.jpg&h=5f180e39&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">萬眾期待，三大核彈全面進場</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3eb1ec2c89d8055d5a682cd0c11c62568a6fdbd5","tid":1508391,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:44:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08cc7e46000df1643ea020fb17ca5e75aa8aead7","tid":1508391,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"[9．1機場] 文宣集合 2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507880</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=4f86d88c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAp4ft3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAp4ft3.jpg&h=2a9e5a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJK4ft3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJK4ft3.jpg&h=2ab03403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1GijVJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1GijVJ.png&h=ecffc0d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b753ff698031f652bfab67cb5752d9289a91b6b","tid":1508391,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de212c9e37d716a233c322c352741e188c883a94","tid":1508391,"uid":191271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>第一大核彈</strong><br />\n香港國際機場 - 世界春袋</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jx8ksg7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjx8ksg7.jpg&h=20079797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港機場對世界、中国、香港黎講<br />\n係一隻會生金蛋既鵝。</span></div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">一： 812 癱瘓機場後全世界國際新聞+媒體+電視台報道，全部有公信力既報紙頭版（NY, CNN,BBC,數唔撚哂），之後有極多外媒黎香港做live (825+826）<br />\n二：國際政府自始高度關注，美英加澳政府發表聲明，令香港問題正式升溫到國際層面。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《CNN》：香港機場關閉，812當日損失數千萬美元</div></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiLnFFu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiLnFFu.jpg&h=75b6fdba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">812啟示 : 無需佔領, 因已癱瘓機場交通</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d3Nxixy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd3Nxixy.jpg&h=3259269f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 控制塔職員、 機師、機場員工返唔到工，沒路入，想問邊個開到機走?  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">入機場方法:<br />\n<br />\n機鐵: 循環線 (機場&gt;香港站&gt;機場&gt;香港站,不停loop) <br />\n馬路: 得一條 <br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議: 某星期六日中午起, 流水式人車海湧入機場消費</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fMFnFGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfMFnFGZ.jpg&h=eb4dd89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場永遠係攬炒首選。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">老豆: 我眼中得狗屋宿舍先係</span>"},{"pid":"e3f0c9aa3bd0280204a24e7b86b92b23cc8409f0","tid":1508391,"uid":190858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[核彈文宣]828#ProtestToo集會全世界都要去 平權=反極權 將火源燒開去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBRCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBRCw.jpg&h=c9bbcd64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aa981867fc5544aca34ffe99a970f8746f813b5","tid":1508391,"