t」意指英國脫歐，Britain＋Exit＝Brexit<br />\n呢個字係點樣吹出黎? 沒錯, 就係用Twitter<br />\n</span></span><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>1.</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先開同我follow 哂下面<br />\n<br />\n全部人, 全部都有幫香港講過野, 全部人都有好撚大影響力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(實在有太多人值得follow，我搵唔哂，希望有巴打係樓下補充)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=efffd5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump</a><br />\n美國總統 - President Donald.J. Trump <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=4cca55c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi</a><br />\nNancy Pelosi - Speaker of the House<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gopleader\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgopleader&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=dfae11d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gopleader</a><br />\nKevin McCarthy - GOPLeader<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=dabeeb92\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr</a><br />\nLeader McConnell - U.S. Senate Majority Leader<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/robert_spalding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frobert_spalding&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=e02da6c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/robert_spalding</a><br />\nGen (Ret) Rob Spalding <br />\n<b